data.description: Solid Greystone 3 unit building located in the North Lawndale community. The property consists of Two 3 bedroom units with 1 bath and a 1 bedroom unit with 1 bath in the garden unit. Property is fully occupied, great opportunity for investors, this is a turn-key transaction. Newer roof within last 18 months, and a new water boiler also newly installed within the last 24 months. Property has a generous space for backyard activities, as well as a parking slab for 2 cars or more. Property being sold "As-Is", seller is motivated!
